title: Who is Kevin Warsh? Secret White House meeting with Trump that made him lead Fed Chair race
summary_full: Kevin Warsh is the top choice to become the next Federal Reserve Chair. President Donald Trump is expected to announce his decision soon. This potential change is creating market buzz and debate about the Fed's future. Warsh's views on monetary policy and economic strategy are key. His nomination could signal a shift in US economic direction.
